{
  "texts": [
    "Then, they convened to share and discuss their codes and refined them.",
    "This process of independent coding and follow-up negotiation was repeated until a consensus was reached on the final set of codes to label the prompts.",
    "Next, based on the prompt labels, the researchers independently determined the interaction profiles for each student, followed by a discussion to establish the final profiles.",
    "Throughout the coding and profiling process, a collaborative Google Spreadsheet was used, which facilitated the coordination and mutual control of coding accuracy.",
    "For the second research question, examining the impact of different AI integration interventions on students' AI interaction profiles, the McNemar-Bowker test (Krampe & Kuhnt, 2007) was conducted."
  ]
}